    "lore": {
        "shortDescription": "You always have certain spells prepared.",
        "fullText": "The Trickery domain grants you access to a set of domain spells at each cleric level listed in the Trickery Domain Spells table. Once you gain a domain spell, you always have it prepared, and it doesn't count against the number of spells you can prepare each day."
    },
